<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 yé sū dài wǒ men lái dào xī shuǐ páng, yě zài nà qīng qīng de cǎo chǎng shàng.
 yáng guāng zhào yào, líng fēng chuī, shén yǔ rén tóng jū de de fāng,
 wǒ men tóng shēng gē chàng hā lì lù yà, wǒ men qí lái zàn měi sòng yáng.
 gān lín xià jiàng, gān lín xià jiàng, gān lín xià jiàng.</lyrics>
<title>gān lín xià jiàng 迦南115</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
